text: This was the sixth season of Barnes Football Club. ==Athletic Sports== * Date: 28 March 1868 * Venue: Field belonging to J. Johnstone, The White Hart, Mortlake. * Committee: A. D. Houseman (starter), F. W. Bryant, R. W. Willis (judges), R. G. Graham (secretary, clerk of course). * Events: 100 yards race, three-quarters of a mile handicap, 440 yards handicap, 220 yards hurdle race, one mile handicap steeplechase, high jump, high jump with pole, long jump ==Notes== Category:Barnes F.C. seasons Barnes
title: 1867–68 Barnes F.C. season
